  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="errores-cool-titulo"/></title>
    <p>[++++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Students select 100 or 170 as the closest multiple of 100 or 10 to 162.</p>
  </paragraphs>


  <!-- Estrategia de apoyo si muchos estudiantes respondieron incorrectamente -->
  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="apoyo-cool-titulo"/></title>
    <p>[++++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>During the launch on the next day’s activity, display 162 on a number line marked with multiples of 10 and 100 and have students discuss the nearest multiple of 10 and 100.</p>
  </paragraphs>

</postlude>

</project>